info.title: Project Demand
info.description:
This service enables you to create, read, update, and delete project demands of enterprise projects and professional services projects. A project demand represents a need for a material, service, resource, or expense that is related to a project or a project element. With this service, you can process the following:
 - Service and material demands of enterprise projects including the related supply information
 - Resource demands of enterprise projects including the related resource assignments
 - Resource demands of professional services projects including the related resource requests and resource assignments with their respective distributions
 - Demands for expenses of professional services projects including the related demand distribution

This service is based on the OData protocol and can be consumed by apps and other user interfaces.

x-sap-shortText: Create, read, update, or delete project demands of enterprise projects and professional services projects using this synchronous inbound service
